      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Good little race. JUST FOR KICKS (3) has just found one better in both starts to date but a maiden win looks imminent, good behind Fatty Finn on debut here before bumping into Rockette last start at Pakenham in a high rating maiden. Looks to have found an ideal race here third up and should get his chance. DUNTULM LASS (7) made good improvement second up going to 1400m at this track, beaten a neck. She should peak now over the extra trip and will take beating. OVERCAST (5) has placed in both starts to date, well backed at Pakenham last time when looking like more ground would suit. Gets that now and he should be very hard to hold out. POSH DIAMANTE (10) has placed in both runs back from a spell and should appreciate rising in trip now, keep safe. STONEAGE ROMEO (6) is off a long spell, watch the betting.",
